    <item>
      <title>Expedia 公布盈利超出预期，但警告需求疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/expedia-warns-of-soft-demand-even-as-it-posts-an-earnings-beat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Expedia Group Inc. 公布了好于预期的第二季度业绩，同时警告本季度旅游需求“疲软”，导致其调整了对今年剩余时间的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/expedia-warns-of-soft-demand-even-as-it-posts-an-earnings-beat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 20:10:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>派拉蒙承担 60 亿美元电视网络费用，加入华纳兄弟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/paramount-takes-6-billion-tv-network-charge-joins-warner-bros</link>
      <description><![CDATA[派拉蒙全球公司是尼克国际儿童频道、MTV 和其他频道的母公司，该公司第二季度对其有线电视网络计提了 59.8 亿美元的减值准备，这再次表明传统电视行业表现疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/paramount-takes-6-billion-tv-network-charge-joins-warner-bros</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 20:00:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股价上涨，华纳兄弟股价暴跌 | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-08/stocks-push-higher-and-warner-brothers-plunges-bloomberg-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Ed Ludlow 观察了在经济衰退担忧消退的情况下股市上涨的情况。此外，华纳兄弟在减记 91 亿美元后股价暴跌，在太空中度过近 60 天后，NASA 制定了一项应急计划，将星际客机机组人员带回地球。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-08/stocks-push-higher-and-warner-brothers-plunges-bloomberg-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 19:13:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
